404
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:50,580
As predicted,

405
00:24:50,580 --> 00:24:52,380
Lu Zegang now trusts Liu Wan'er.

406
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:57,460
Did Prince Yu

407
00:24:57,620 --> 00:25:00,660
(Prudent in Thought, Diligent in Action)
send the impostor

408
00:25:01,060 --> 00:25:02,980
to destroy evidence of Mr Su's case

409
00:25:02,980 --> 00:25:04,660
in Lu Zegang's possession,

410
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:08,300
and even to eliminate Lu Zegang?

411
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:09,780
Correct.

412
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:12,380
If this evidence disappears,

413
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:14,100
our chance to overthrow Prince Yu

414
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,660
will also disappear.

415
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,660
But I suspect Prince Yu's ambitions

416
00:25:20,060 --> 00:25:21,060
run deeper.

417
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:23,500
You're suggesting

418
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:24,620
that this plot

419
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:26,900
is not just against Lu Zegang?

420
00:25:28,780 --> 00:25:31,660
Lu Zegang is the Minister of Works.

421
00:25:32,260 --> 00:25:33,080
Recently,

422
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:35,280
the Ministry of Works has been preparing
for the Blessing Ceremony.

423
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:36,220
With the impostor

424
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:38,500
free to hold charity events

425
00:25:38,900 --> 00:25:40,700
at the venue

426
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:43,300
and Prince Rui scheduled...

427
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:46,260
He was scheduled to ascend the altar.

428
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:49,380
Prince Yu plans to kill Prince Rui

429
00:25:49,430 --> 00:25:50,330
during the ceremony.

430
00:25:54,420 --> 00:25:55,550
No wonder His Majesty's assignment

431
00:25:55,580 --> 00:25:57,380
of this honor

432
00:25:57,380 --> 00:25:58,580
to Prince Rui

433
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:01,580
has met with no opposition.

434
00:26:01,940 --> 00:26:02,900
At that time,

435
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:04,820
should Prince Rui perish,

436
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:06,540
Lu Zegang would face

437
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:08,100
execution and clan extinction.

438
00:26:09,300 --> 00:26:11,500
A masterful two-birds-one-stone trick.

439
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:15,100
(Top Scholar Residence)

440
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:15,940
Tangli,

441
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:18,020
I know you're staying

442
00:26:18,020 --> 00:26:19,420
with Prince Yu

443
00:26:20,260 --> 00:26:21,580
for revenge,

444
00:26:22,780 --> 00:26:24,460
but he's too cunning.

445
00:26:25,100 --> 00:26:26,900
You must be careful.

446
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:29,620
Rest assured, Mr. Lu.

447
00:26:29,780 --> 00:26:30,900
I have my own measurements.

448
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:34,380
But

449
00:26:35,300 --> 00:26:36,340
even if we have proof

450
00:26:36,340 --> 00:26:38,300
that Prince Yu harmed my father,

451
00:26:39,100 --> 00:26:40,860
can we really overthrow him?

452
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,620
Trust Da'an's laws

453
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,860
to punish evil,

454
00:26:47,900 --> 00:26:48,980
and justice

455
00:26:49,540 --> 00:26:50,380
to prevail

456
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:51,860
in the hearts of people.

457
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,780
I hope so.

458
00:26:58,700 --> 00:27:04,460
(Top Scholar Residence)

459
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:12,540
What?

460
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:14,860
Wan'er serves Prince Yu?

461
00:27:15,540 --> 00:27:16,380
That's right.

462
00:27:17,380 --> 00:27:18,540
Minister Lu, you wanted

463
00:27:18,540 --> 00:27:19,900
to use your daughter

464
00:27:19,900 --> 00:27:21,260
as political capital,

465
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:23,460
but instead,

466
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,700
you became

467
00:27:24,700 --> 00:27:26,300
someone else's pawn.

468
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:32,260
Reviewer Lu,

469
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:33,820
you didn't just come

470
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:35,780
to mock me, right?

471
00:27:37,140 --> 00:27:38,100
Now you're trapped

472
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:39,820
in Prince Yu's web,

473
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,500
facing execution

474
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:43,460
or clan annihilation

475
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:45,380
as the Minister of Works

476
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:47,380
if Prince Rui dies

477
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:48,580
during

478
00:27:49,050 --> 00:27:50,460
the ceremony.

479
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,420
Your only recourse

480
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:54,300
is to

481
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:57,020
join us

482
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:58,260
and overthrow Prince Yu.

483
00:27:58,860 --> 00:28:00,620
Maybe you'll survive.

484
00:28:04,940 --> 00:28:06,060
Overthrow him?

485
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:08,220
But how?

486
00:28:09,340 --> 00:28:10,900
Why should I trust you?

487
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:15,340
Trust me

488
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:18,300
means survival.

489
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:21,180
Refusal means...

490
00:28:27,620 --> 00:28:28,860
That's all.

491
00:28:30,340 --> 00:28:31,180
Reviewer Lu,

492
00:28:35,700 --> 00:28:37,580
I'll do as you say.

493
00:28:38,540 --> 00:28:40,020
After the Blessing Ceremony,

494
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:42,940
I'll provide proof
that Prince Yu framed Su Changhua.

495
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:44,020
But

496
00:28:44,860 --> 00:28:46,300
you have to make sure

497
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:48,420
that in return,

498
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:51,260
Prince Rui must keep his promise

499
00:28:51,260 --> 00:28:53,700
and guarantee my clan's safety.

500
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:00,540
Deal.

501
00:29:11,210 --> 00:29:12,220
So Prince Yu

502
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:14,700
would sacrifice brotherly ties

503
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:17,300
for this plan.

504
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,020
Now that his dagger

505
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:21,180
is out of its sheath,

506
00:29:22,020 --> 00:29:23,580
we can expose

507
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,730
his crimes

508
00:29:26,090 --> 00:29:27,100
with a counter-strike.

509
00:29:30,330 --> 00:29:31,440
But risks remain,

510
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:33,500
and our plans

511
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:35,100
may be flawed.

512
00:29:56,500 --> 00:30:01,700
(Yongjing Terrace)

513
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:10,740
Stop!

514
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:17,100
(Minister of Works)

515
00:30:22,700 --> 00:30:24,020
For the Blessing Ceremony,

516
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:25,940
three main streets around the altar

517
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,020
are sealed off.

518
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:29,020
Only authorized personnel

519
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:30,860
can enter,

520
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:32,060
with heavy guards

521
00:30:32,060 --> 00:30:33,140
at each entrance.

522
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,660
The altar is heavily guarded.

523
00:30:41,300 --> 00:30:43,340
Marshal personally oversees security.

524
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:46,900
Officials undergo

525
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:49,420
multiple checks.

526
00:30:49,540 --> 00:30:50,460
Commoners can only

527
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:51,700
worship on the periphery

528
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,100
on that day.

529
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:54,580
They'll be unable to access.

530
00:30:55,340 --> 00:30:56,260
Security

531
00:30:56,260 --> 00:30:57,100
seems assured.

532
00:31:03,540 --> 00:31:06,340
(Yongjing Terrace, Observation Deck,
