00:31:26,580 --> 00:31:28,780
(Observation Deck)

536
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:30,500
The observation deck.

537
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:33,300
That's right.

538
00:31:33,780 --> 00:31:34,620
Prince Yu is probably

539
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:36,300
planning an ambush here.

540
00:31:36,540 --> 00:31:37,780
Tightened defences

541
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:39,020
