542
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:48,820
(Altar)

543
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:55,620
(Altar)

544
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:05,300
(Altar)

545
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,340
What's wrong?

546
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:23,660
Now that

547
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:25,540
you know Prince Yu's intentions,

548
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:27,380
you must have plans.

549
00:32:28,300 --> 00:32:29,500
I've been waiting for you to tell me.

550
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:35,340
If you've made your decision,

551
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:36,700
then act on it.

552
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:38,980
I won't stop you.

553
00:32:42,540 --> 00:32:44,380
I'll make
all the necessary preparations,

554
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:47,380
but I'll need

555
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:50,100
your help.

556
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:52,740
Will you stand by me?

557
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:07,140
(Lu Chang,)

558
00:33:08,580 --> 00:33:09,980
(just do it.)

559
00:33:11,660 --> 00:33:13,420
