560
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:29,180
Rituals require ceremonial cleansing

561
00:33:29,300 --> 00:33:30,940
and proper attire.

562
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:33,020
Let me quickly iron
this ceremonial robe for you.

563
00:33:37,020 --> 00:33:37,860
Mingshu,

564
00:33:46,460 --> 00:33:47,300
enough.

565
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:56,740
Let me look at you.

566
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:59,540
What is there to see?
You see me every day.

567
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:03,340
This is different.

568
00:34:06,420 --> 00:34:07,340
Today is different.

569
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,380
I know what you're going to say.

570
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:18,260
Remember what I said.

571
00:34:19,890 --> 00:34:20,900
Did you remember?

572
00:34:48,770 --> 00:34:51,320
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

