00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:23,260
♪Through years with sincere love♪

582
00:35:23,260 --> 00:35:26,420
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

583
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:29,990
♪Counting endless nights♪

